description: Lists the profiles associated with your Amazon Web Services account for your current or specified region. A profile is the mechanism used to create the concept of a private network.

nested_items.name: profiles
nested_items.description: Returns an array of ProfileSummary objects.

nested_items.name: profileId
nested_items.description: Returns the unique, system-generated identifier for the profile.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: Returns the display name for profile.

nested_items.name: businessName
nested_items.description: Returns the name for the business associated with this profile.

nested_items.name: logging
nested_items.description: Specifies whether or not logging is enabled for this profile.

nested_items.name: logGroupName
nested_items.description: Returns the name of the logging group.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: Returns the timestamp for creation date and time of the profile.

nested_items.name: modifiedAt
nested_items.description: Returns the timestamp that identifies the most recent date and time that the profile was modified.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: When additional results are obtained from the command, a NextToken parameter is returned in the output. You can then pass the NextToken parameter in a subsequent command to continue listing additional resources.
